code: @Override public void process(Exchange exchange) throws Exception {     Object body = exchange.getIn().getBody().     if (body instanceof Key) {         Value v = keyValue.get((Key) body).         exchange.getOut().setBody(v).     }     if (body instanceof Object[]) {         Object[] args = (Object[]) body.         if (args.length == 1 && args[0] instanceof Key) {             Value v = keyValue.get((Key) args[0]).             exchange.getOut().setBody(v).         }     } }
public void setKeyValue(KeyValueProtocol keyValue) {     this.keyValue = keyValue. }
